did.head: Collection Summary

repository.corpname: Woodson Research Center, Rice University, Houston, Texas

did.unittitle: Rice University Past faculty and staff records
did.abstract: Correspondence, memoranda, and reports relating to faculty and professional employees no longer associated with Rice University. Includes permanent and temporary appointments.

bioghist.head: Biographical / Historical
bioghist.p: Rice University opened in October 1912 as the Rice Institute.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Correspondence, memoranda, and reports relating to faculty and professional employees no longer associated with Rice University. Includes permanent and temporary appointments.

accessrestrict.head: Access Restrictions
accessrestrict.p: This material is restricted. Permission to access these records must be obtained from the Rice University President's office.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Stored off-site at the Library Service Center. Please request this material via woodson@rice.edu or call 713-348-2586.

userestrict.head: Use Restrictions
userestrict.p: Permission to publish from this material must be obtained from Woodson Research Center, Fondren Library, Rice University.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: This material was transferred to Woodson Research Center in 1968; 1989-90; July, 1991; July, 1992; and June, 1996.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Rice University Past Faculty and Staff Records, 1968-1996, UA 008, Woodson Research Center, Fondren Library, Rice University.

odd.head: General Note
odd.p: The following files except for the first are organized by alphabet. Each letter contains two groups of files: one for staff and administration and the other for fellows and research associates. The dates on each file correspond to the date of the materials within the files. The exact working dates of the individuals are unknown. While there are some coaches files in Series I, there also some located in this series.
